# Normalized low-poly navigation buoy collision shell.
# Derived from generate_maritime_world.py navigation_buoy_model proportions:
# tapered body, wider band shoulders, and a smaller top cap.
# Scene scale maps x/y to buoy radius and z to buoy height.
mtllib navigation_buoy_collision.mtl
o navigation_buoy_collision_shell
usemtl buoy_yellow
